# Document Counter Application

An automatic document counting application that processes various document formats and provides statistics on page counts, word counts, and character counts.

## Features

- **Multi-format Support**: Process PDF, Word (DOCX), Excel (XLSX), Images (JPG, PNG, TIFF), and Text files
- **Automatic Counting**: Count pages, words, and characters automatically
- **OCR Support**: Extract text from images using Tesseract OCR
- **Web Interface**: Clean, responsive web interface for file upload and management
- **Database Storage**: SQLite database for tracking all documents
- **Statistics Dashboard**: View overall statistics and document details
- **Export Functionality**: Export document data to CSV format
- **Real-time Processing**: Instant document processing and counting

## Supported Formats

| Format | Extensions | Counts |
|--------|------------|--------|
| PDF | .pdf | Pages, Words, Characters |
| Word | .docx | Pages (approx), Words, Characters |
| Excel | .xlsx, .xls | Sheets, Words |
| Images | .jpg, .jpeg, .png, .tiff | Pages (1), Words (OCR) |
| Text | .txt, .md, .csv | Pages (approx), Words, Characters |

## Installation

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.8 or higher
- Tesseract OCR (for image text extraction)

### Install Tesseract OCR

**Windows:**
Download from: https://github.com/UB-Mannheim/tesseract/wiki

**Linux:**
```bash
sudo apt-get install tesseract-ocr